name: Chris Hart
text: The manager Cassie is top notch. She makes a person's experience very enjoyable. 5 star all the way for her.

name: Jim Hansen
text: The servier was excellent.  Food ordered was  accurate,  hot & tasty. My family was quiet pleased so we will make a point of returning often. Thks

name: Cameron Spink
text: The store just changed ownership, and they don't deliver anywhere around Chittenango. I live like 2 miles from them, and they all the sudden can't bring a pizza right down the road. If I was to get into my truck and go out into the winter I wouldn't waste my time on Pizza hut!

name: Wendy Matters
text: The customer service does not even rate 1 star. Be careful ordering online, what you select is not what they receive apparently.  Yes, they fixed my order at no cost just to then call me at 10:30 PM (3.5 hours later) to tell me I was wrong. â€¦More

name: Matt
text: They are out of business. Not much more to say  now, proof is right there.

name: Rachel D.
text: I went with my family and we sat and waited atleast 20 minutes before we even got drinks. The woman at the table next to us advised us to just order online and it would take the same amount of time... She was right. The interior is shabby, the staff could be a bit more friendly. I don't think I'll be going back.

name: Brenda Sharp
text: Was very nice today. Pleasant service . Clean Restaraunt.

name: Cherie Crossway
text: The Chittenango  pizza hut is the best one to visit , Great workers and good food

name: Cody Quick
text: Food is great and fast and the manager is always there to help and make your stay enjoyable highly recommend going

name: Jonathan Darling
text: I love how nice the employees are and the pizza is really good

name: Jordan Scheid
text: They just simply suck. Forget sauce every single time. Never get the order right. Half the times its the wrong pizza. Online order is stupid and is always screwing up especially when the food is ready to be picked up

name: Ang
text: Ok food for an ok price. make sure you check your food before you leave because they often mess up or forget things.

name: Fred Knowlton
text: Dan was awesome! Excellent food and service! Thank you!

name: Dustin Cross
text: Fast service at this location, decent pizza overall. Staff is friendly

name: Erik Rik
text: Great serve and a reasonable price when I was there.

name: Jeffrey Smith
text: Good food. Great service.

name: Cassie Mudge
text: Fast food hot nice upgrades to surrondings great people

name: Kelly Vollmer
text: My order was wrong. They remade my whole order only to get home and find my still wrong. Very disappointing

name: Tina Tillotson
text: Great prices hot food

name: andy bak
text: Tasty food, ok price, we like the new menus.

name: Tanner Dewolf
text: Quick service during lunch. A pizza hut is a pizza hut but this one was clean and had friendly staff.

text:
No service ordered food got it never saw a waiter ever again had to go ask for more drinks
Will never go there agin
